summary: An Ordinance providing for the purchase of portions of Lots Three (3) and Four (4), Block Forty-six (46); and portions of Lots ten (10), Eleven (11) and Twelve (12), Block Forty-four (44), Yesler's Third Addition to the City of Seattle, for park and parkway purposes, for a sum not to exceed Thirty-five Hundred Dollars ($3,500.00).
